HEADWORD: fortuneteller
<hw>for"tune*tel`ler</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a person who claims to be
able to foretell events in the future of another person.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> fortune teller, fortune-teller.</syn>⟦br⟧
